<i>But 20 minutes? Absolutely.</i>

13:11.458 --> 13:14.759
Barry, the cop just said
he's gonna tow the car!

13:14.761 --> 13:16.494
Well, I would, too!

13:16.496 --> 13:16.961
God!

13:16.963 --> 13:20.565
