20:49.515 --> 20:51.849
(CHUCKLES) Classic.

20:53.352 --> 20:56.120
<i>(CENTERFOLD</i> PLAYING)

20:56.888 --> 20:58.856
<i>♪ Come on</i>

21:03.195 --> 21:05.096
You're aggravating me,
you little bastards!

