He's aggravating me,
the little bastard!

21:07.767 --> 21:10.501
The sexiest man alive?
Yes, I do.

21:10.503 --> 21:12.470
Look what I'm
drinking tonight.

21:12.472 --> 21:13.471
Don't forget to wash
your bottom.

21:13.473 --> 21:16.440
I don't believe you.
You're really a jackass.

21:16.442 --> 21:20.211
Stop videotaping!
Get out! Mom!

21:20.213 --> 21:23.147
Stop! I swear...
